[src:gcp-apigee/service-oriented-architecture] However, as of 2008, use-cases demonstrated the potential of combining technologies and principles of both Web 2.0 and SOA.
[src:gcp-apigee/service-oriented-architecture] Microservices are a modern interpretation of service-oriented architectures used to build distributed software systems.
[src:gcp-apigee/service-oriented-architecture] Services in a microservice architecture are processes that communicate with each other over the network in order to fulfill a goal.
